# Manga Image Downloader

Using specific url for download manga pictures to specific directory.

Default directory set by current directory and inside assets dir. If you are going to running this script in /home/james it will create /home/james/assets directory and put contents in this directory.

Scripts needs three parameters;
1 - Site Name
2 - Site Serach Name
3 - After search listed maximum manga content

    chmod +x jpg-downloader.sh
    ./jpg-downloader www.mangasite.com dragon-ball 35
